(IMAGE PLACEMENT TIP: An easy way to center a picture exactly how you want is to crop it before uploading to the Zazzle website.) This template includes graduate name, class year & school, and is simple to customize with any wording of your choice, such as party invitation details, parents’ names, special honors, degree title, favorite inspirational quote, graduate’s contact info, future education plans, or new job position. If there’s any text not wanted simply delete it. Design features a dark blue brushed background, faux foil mortar board cap, handwritten style script calligraphy, modern minimalist typography, and two photos of your choice, such as senior pictures or images from the commencement ceremony. Please note that gold is printed color, not metallic foil. These elegant graduation announcement cards are a stylish way to share your special day celebration with family and friends.
